{
  "texts": [
    "And then the overfitting is reduced by Dropout.",
    "Image-EncoderThe Image-Encoder module utilizes an adapter layer fine-tuned on the CLIP image encoder to extract global features from the image.",
    "The parameters of the pretrained CLIP model are frozen, with only the adapter layer trained on the BUUISE-Image traffic scene dataset.",
    "This approach ensures the generalization of the CLIP model while significantly reducing CLIP model training costs.",
    "The image encoder is depicted in Figure 3."
  ]
}